description: Are you a fan of pork tenderloins?  Then you my friend just hit the jackpot! To find the best breaded pork tenderloin in this planet then look no further than Chuckies. Chuckies specializes in breaded pork tenderloin using nothing but the finest cut of pork available on the market. Made using their secret batter and breading mix, Chuckies has developed their own world famous recipe known as "Chuckies Tenderloins."
name: Chuckies
